%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Barden%20as%20young%20Valya%20Harkonnen%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Prophecy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAttila%20Szvacsek%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e6eccec-7f11-4afc-87ba-6605dab28ca0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sisterhood%20of%20Dune'%20is%20a%20prequel%20novel%20set%20in%20the%20'Dune'%20universe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20Herbert's%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20novels%20compose%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20franchise.%20Following%20his%20death%20in%201986%2C%20his%20son%20Brian%20and%20Anderson%20began%20publishing%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20prequel%20novels%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSisterhood%20of%20Dune%26quot%3B%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BGreat%20Schools%20of%20Dune%26quot%3B%20prequel%20series%20written%20by%20the%20two%2C%20and%20it%20was%20published%20in%202012.%20It's%20set%2083%20years%20after%20humanity's%20victory%20over%20the%20thinking%20machines%2C%20and%20as%20the%20title%20suggests%2C%20covers%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Sisterhood.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Raquella%20Berto-Anirul%20survives%20a%20poisoning%20that%20unlocks%20her%20genetic%20memory%2C%20she%20becomes%20the%20first%20Reverend%20Mother.%20That%20process%2C%20dubbed%20the%20Spice%20Agony%2C%20killed%20a%20number%20of%20sisters%20who%20were%20unable%20to%20withstand%20the%20poison%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20it%20eventually%20turned%20others%20into%20Reverend%20Mothers%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaquella%20trains%20Valya%2C%20a%20daughter%20of%20the%20war-disgraced%20Harkonnen%20family%2C%20and%20lets%20her%20in%20on%20the%20Sisterhood's%20tightest-held%20secret%3A%20It%20uses%20computer%20technology%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20genetic%20database%20necessary%20for%20the%20organization's%20breeding%20program.%20(As%20established%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20movies%2C%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20that%20breeding%20program%20was%20to%20produce%20a%20male%20Reverend%20Mother%20known%20as%20the%20Kwisatz%20Haderach%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20this%20show%2C%20don't%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20that.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20novel%20also%20features%20other%20characters%20including%20Manford%20Torondo%2C%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20anti-technology%20Butlerian%20movement%2C%20and%20Vorian%20Atreides%2C%20a%20war%20hero.%20From%20the%20royal%20family%2C%20there's%20Emperor%20Salvatore%20Corrino%20and%20his%20half-siblings%20Roderick%20and%20Anna.%20Valya's%20brother%20Griffin%20is%20also%20present%2C%20and%20there%20are%20mentions%20of%20her%20younger%20sister%20Tula%2C%20who%20features%20prominently%20in%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20important%20sister%20in%20the%20book%20as%20well%3A%20Doretea%2C%20who%20succeeds%20in%20becoming%20the%20second-ever%20Reverend%20Mother%20after%20Raquella.%20She%20and%20Valya%20are%20at%20odds%2C%20however%2C%20and%20Doretea%20puts%20the%20Sisterhood's%20mission%20in%20jeopardy%20by%20revealing%20the%20existence%20of%20its%20thinking%20machine%20to%20the%20Emperor.%20The%20sisterhood%20is%20forced%20to%20relocate%20and%20rebuild%20on%20the%20planet%20Wallach%20IX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Travis%20Fimmel%20as%20Desmond%20Hart%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Prophecy%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6737c6a3ede4eeae3927fdc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravis%20Fimmel%20as%20Desmond%20Hart%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Prophecy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAttila%20Szvacsek%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249dad0c0-be5c-42cf-afb4-0eb455979aba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Dune%3A%20Prophecy'%20isn't%20an%20exact%20adaptation%20of%20'Sisterhood%20of%20Dune'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20television%20series%20draws%20significantly%20from%20the%20history%20presented%20