-week-panel-to-delhi-other-states-7035767%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epollution%20control%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20under%20Stage%204%20of%20the%20anti-pollution%20plan%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%2C%20which%20have%20come%20into%20effect%20from%208%20am.%20This%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20preventive%20actions%20announced%20under%20Stage%201%2C%20Stage%202%20and%20Stage%203%20of%20GRAP%20already%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhi-pollution-curbs-ban-on-these-vehicles-staggered-office-timings-7031055%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGRAP%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20divided%20into%20four%20stages%20of%20air%20quality%3A%20Stage%201%20for%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20ranging%20from%20201%20to%20300)%2C%20Stage%202%20for%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20from%20301%20to%20400)%2C%20Stage%203%20for%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20from%20401%20to%20450)%2C%20and%20Stage%204%20for%20%26quot%3Bsevere-plus%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20(AQI%20above%20450).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20-%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20-%20has%20urged%20the%20public%2C%20particularly%20children%2C%20senior%20citizens%20and%20those%20with%20respiratory%2C%20cardiovascular%2C%20cerebrovascular%20or%20other%20chronic%20diseases%2C%20to%20stay%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGRAP%204%20In%20Delhi%20As%20Air%20Quality%20Worsens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fgrap-4-in-delhi-delhi-air-pollution-delhi-air-quality-grap-4-in-delhi-explained-what-is-banned-what-is-allowed-7044081%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrap%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20no%20trucks%20will%20be%20allowed%20into%20Delhi%20except%20for%20those%20carrying%20essential