3EAttila%20Szvacsek%2FHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20member%20of%20the%20sisterhood%20is%20Reverend%20Mother%20Kasha%2C%20played%20by%20South%20Korean%20singer%20and%20actor%20Jihae%20in%20the%20present%20day%20scenes%20and%20%26quot%3BBridgerton%26quot%3B%20season%20four%20lead%20Yerin%20Ha%20in%20the%20flashback%20sequences.%20When%20we%20first%20meet%20her%20in%20episode%20one%2C%20Kasha%20is%20serving%20as%20the%20Truthsayer%20(a%20specially%20trained%20sister%20capable%20of%20detecting%20falsehoods%20who's%20assigned%20to%20royal%20houses)%20to%20Emperor%20Javicco%20Corrino%20(Mark%20Strong).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20loyalties%20are%20truly%20to%20the%20sisterhood%20and%20their%20shared%20mission%2C%20Kasha%20formed%20a%20special%20bond%20with%20Corrino's%20daughter%2C%20Princess%20Ynez%2C%20whom%20she'd%20known%20and%20cared%20for%20since%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKasha%20is%20rattled%20when%20she%20has%20a%20shocking%20vision%20about%20Ynez%20in%20the%20premiere%2C%20and%20flees%20back%20to%20the%20sisterhood's%20home%20planet%20Wallach%20IX%2C%20where%20she%20tries%20to%20convince%20Valya%20and%20Tula%20Harkonnen%20that%20danger%20is%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20Valya's%20dismisiveness%2C%20that%20danger%20comes%20by%20the%20episode's%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKasha%20wakes%20screaming%20in%20the%20night%20and%20is%20found%20burning%20to%20death%20from%20the%20inside%20out.%20Kasha's%20death%20leads%20Valya%20to%20conclude%20that%20she's%20witnessing%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20catastrophic%20event%20that%20her%20predecessor%2C%20Reverend%20Mother%20Raquella%20Berto-Anirul%2C%20warned%20about%20on%20her%20death%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20Jihae%20breaks%20down%20her%20big%20scene%2C%20how%20she%20got%20in%20the%20headspace%20to%20burn%20to%20death%2C%20and%20how%20a%20personal%20tragedy%20made%20filming%20the%20moment%20even%20more%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jihae%20as%20Reverend%20Mother%20Kasha%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6737e67ffa0140cdd563e2c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJihae%20as%20Reverend%20Mother%20Kasha.%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20know%20Kasha%20would%20die%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20episode%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20have%20any%20trepidation%20about%20taking%20on%20a%20character%20who%20wouldn't%20be%20around%20very%20long%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20at%20the%20time.%20No%2C%20the%20way%20the%20script%20went%20along%2C%20it%20was%20such%20a%20rich%20journey%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20changed%20since%20I%20accepted%20that%20role%20in%202022%3B%20it%20was%20a%20two-year%20situation.%20But%20I%20have%20to%20say%20that%2C%20as%20difficult%20as%20it%20was%2C%20it%20was%20such%20a%20huge%20learning%20lesson%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20elaborate%20on%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20it%20was%20difficult.%20It's%20never%20easy%20to%20play%20a%20role%20where%20you%20are%20going%20through%20severe%2C%20intense%20physical%20pain%2C%20and%20to%20portray%20that%20in%20a%20realistic%20way%20without%20hurting%20yourself.%20I%20think%20we're%20so%20used%20to%20watching%20violence%20and%20violent%20things%20that%20happen%20in%20shows%2C%20that%20it%20just%20seems%20like%2C%20oh%2C%20it's%20just%20another%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20thousand%20ways%20for%20an%20actor%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20act%2C%20but%20there's%20nothing%20out%20there%20that%20tells%20you%20how%20to%20take%20off%20the%20character%2C%20how%20to%20take%20off%20that%20emotion.%20So%20yeah%2C%20it%20was%20tough.%20It%20was%20tough%20coming%20out.%20It%20was%20tough%20going%20through%20it.%20But%20we%20choose%20these%20challenges%20so%20we%20can%20grow%2C%20and%20I%20definitely%20grew%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221869%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jihae%20as%20Reverend%20Mother%20Kasha%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6737e6f9192f52589858fd49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221402%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReverend%20Mother%20Kasha%20burns%20from%20the%20inside%20out.%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20mentally%20prepare%20to%20get%20into%20that%20headspace%20to%20portray%20that%20kind%20of%20pain%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20believe%20in%20using%20my%20own%20stuff.%20I%20don't%20believe%20in%20Method%20acting.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20really%20cruel%20to%20oneself%2C%20especially%20in%20these%20types%20of%20scenes.%20And%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20Method%20acting%20is%20viable%20at%20all%20when%20you%20are%20doing%20physically%20violent%20things%20in%20the%20scenes%2C%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20here's%20what%20I%20did%3A%20Women%20have%20gone%20through%20so%20much%20pain%20historically%20%E2%80%94%20we%20go%20through%20double%20the%20amount%20of%20pain%20that%20men%20do.%20But%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20having%20our%20rights%2C%20how%20much%20women%20had%20to%20suffer%20for%20suffrage%20and%20for%20just%20basic%20rights%2C%20to%20own%20a%20home%2C%20to%20have%20a%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20be%20a%20portal%20through%20which%20all%20the%20ancestors%20before%20me%2C%20female%20ancestors%2C%20who%20had%20something%20to%20say%2C%20but%20weren't%20able%20to%20say%20it%2C%20who%20had%20all%20this%20angst%20because%20of%20all%20that%20they%20suffered%20%E2%80%94%20I%20decided%20I%20will%20allow%20them%20to%20scream%20through%20me.%20So%20it%20made%20it%20that%20much%20easier%20to%20be%20realistic%2C%20because%20it's%20based%20on%20truth%2C%20it's%20based%20on%20experience.%20That%20actually%20did%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20terms%20of%20aftercare%2C%20how%20did%20you%20come%20down%20from%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20Budapest%20is%20full%20of%20hot%20springs%2C%20and%20I%20love%20going%20to%20those%20places%20and%20just%20letting%20it%20all%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20round%20of%20filming%2C%20it%20was%20end%20of%202022.%20My%20dad%20had%20just%20passed%20away%2C%20and%20so%20it%20was%20even%20more%20intense%20dealing%20with%20all%20that.%20I%20think%20I%20was%20able%20to%20just%20do%20the%20deed%2C%20the%20number%20of%20days%20it%20took%2C%20and%20then%20just%20had%20a%20wonderful%2C%20wonderful%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20days%20were%20you%20filming%20that%20scene%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20three%20to%20four%20days.%20My%20body%20just%20started%20revolting.%20When%20I%20got%20the%20news%20that%20they're%20adding%20a%20day%2C%20my%20body%20was%20just%20shaking.%20It's%20like%2C%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20the%20death%20the%20last%20thing%20you%20shot%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Efirst%3C%2Fem%3E%20thing%20I%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20was%20added%20later.%20I%20actually%20requested%2C%20could%20I%20please%20be%20at%20my%20powerful%20first%20when%20she%20first%20appears%2C%20and%20then%20she%20did%20that%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20no%20chance%20of%20accommodating%20any%20of%20that%2C%20just%20because%20I%20had%20to%20be%20absent%20for%20five%20months%20due%20to%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20you%20signed%20on%20back%20in%202022%2C%20what%20was%20your%20familiarity%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20universe%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20movie.%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20the%20book%2C%20and%20then%20I%20learned%20that%20it%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20book%2C%20but%20not%20taken%20from%20the%20book.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20and%20research%20more%20about%20F