C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20we%20all%20knew%20Sachin%20could%20never%20be%20replaced.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20play%20against%20both%20Indian%20legends%20in%20all%20formats%20and%20while%20there%20are%20some%20similarities%2C%20they%20were%20also%20very%20different.%20One%20of%20Kohli's%20attributes%20stood%20out%20early%20to%20me%20above%20all%20others%20-%20he%20was%20up%20for%20the%20fight!%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20wrote%20in%20his%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewest.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fmitchell-johnson-how-virat-kohli-changed-the-face-of-indian-cricket-as-the-games-next-big-thing-c-16764879%5C%22%3EThe%20West%20Australian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20kind%20of%20aggressive%20attitude%20was%20something%20we%20had%20rarely%20seen%20from%20an%20Indian%20player%20at%20that%20point.%20We%20were%20used%20to%20giving%20it%20but%20didn't%20always%20get%20it%20back%20in%20return.%20While%20the%20occasional%20player%20from%20India%20may%20have%20been%20combative%20in%20moments%2C%20Kohli%20really%20made%20it%20a%20part%20of%20his%20game.%20He%20took%20his%20team%20with%20him%20as%20well%20so%20it's%20not%20an%20understatement%20to%20say%20that%20Kohli%20changed%20the%20face%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20taking%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20players%20and%20showing%20them%20how%20to%20play%20tough%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20recalled%20the%202014-15%20series%20against%20India%20where%20Kohli%20did%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20scoring%2C%20even%20though%20Australia%20won%20the%20four%20match%20series%202-0.%20Johnson%20also%20said%20he%20had%20a%20personal%20rivalry%20with%20Kohli%2C%20but%20he%20enjoyed%20every%20minute%20of%20their%20duels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20hearing%20at%20the%20back%20end%20of%20Tendulkar%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virender%20Sehwag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers