ert's%20son%2C%20Brian%20Herbert%2C%20and%20Kevin%20J.%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20direct%20adaptation%20of%20the%20trilogy%2C%20but%20it%20pulls%20characters%20and%20storylines%20from%20the%20three%20books%2C%20which%20were%20published%20between%202012%20and%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20also%20notes%20that%20it%20takes%20place%20%26quot%3B116%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20great%20machine%20wars.%26quot%3B%20Fans%20will%20know%20that%20this%20refers%20to%20an%20event%20that%20shaped%20the%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20universe%20in%20a%20very%20specific%20way.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BButlerian%20Jihad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220036f7f5-1082-4300-82f0-daaddfcba0fd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Butlerian%20Jihad%3F%20'Dune%3A%20Prophecy'%20explains%20the%20revolution%20against%20'thinking%20machines'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandworms%20attacking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ddfc7c6080194819fa6e26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Part%202.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series'%20opening%20includes%20a%20brief%20look%20at%20the%20forces%20of%20humanity%20fighting%20against%20massive%20machines%2C%20giving%20fans%20the%20first%20depiction%20of%20the%20Butlerian%20Jihad%20in%20live%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Butlerian%20Jihad%20was%20the%20revolution%20against%20robots%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20which%20the%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20universe%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20machines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20books%2C%20this%20happened%20because%20Omnius%2C%20the%20robotic%20ruler%20of%20the%20Synchronized%20Empire%2C%20had%20overthrown%20several%20planets%20in%20the%20universe%2C%20and%20there%20were%20fears%20that%20the%