20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20Barapula%20Elevated%20Corridor%20Phase-3%20in%20front%20of%20Mayur%20Vihar%20Phase-1%2C%20Yamuna%20Khadar%2C%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20four%20new%20hospitals%20across%20the%20national%20capital%20will%20likely%20be%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERestrictions%20under%20GRAP-4%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20GRAP-4%2C%20a%20ban%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20Delhi-registered%20BS-IV%20or%20older%20diesel%20medium%20and%20heavy%20goods%20vehicles.%20All%20trucks%20and%20light%20commercial%20vehicles%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20except%20for%20those%20carrying%20essential%20commodities%20or%20providing%20essential%20services%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20all%20schools%20have%20been%20shifted%20online%2C%20except%20for%20Classes%2010%20and%2012.%20Public%20and%20private%20offices%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20work%20at%2050%20per%20cent%20capacity%20and%20the%20rest%20have%20been%20recommended%20to%20work%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20government%20release%2C%20the%20state%20government%20may%20consider%20additional%20emergency%20measures%20such%20as%20the%20closure%20of%20non-emergency%20commercial%20activities%2C%20and%20permitting%20the%20running%20of%20vehicles%20on%20an%20odd-even%20basis%20of%20registration%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731896160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fr7695oo_delhi-air_625x300_17_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-how-grap-4-anti-pollution-curbs-may-impact-major-projects-in-delhi-7044007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi's%20air%20quality%20plunged%20to%20'severe%20plus'%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20year%20on%20Sunday%20night%2C%20forcing%20the%20government%20to%20implemen