20from%20real%20people%20while%20highlighting%20the%20need%20for%20consumers%20to%20stay%20vigilant%20as%20the%20UK%20faces%20a%20fraud%20epidemic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20worldwide.%20Almost%201%20in%203%20Americans%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-scams-fraud-liability-banks-government-ftc-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20victim%20of%20a%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20with%20an%20average%20loss%20of%20%241%2C600%20a%20person%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20from%20IPX%2C%20a%20financial%20analysis%20firm.%20According%20to%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20consumers%20reported%20more%20than%20%2410%20billion%20in%20losses%20last%20year%20from%20online%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Media%20O2%20says%20it%20decided%20to%20create%20Daisy%20after%20conducting%20research%20that%20showed%20that%2071%25%20of%20Brits%20wanted%20to%20retaliate%20against%20scammers%20but%20that%20most%20of%20them%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20time%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20company%20partnered%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20scambaiters%20on%20YouTube%2C%20Jim%20Browning%2C%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20chatbot.%20Browning%20is%20known%20for%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20clueless%20victim%20long%20enough%20to%20frustrate%20scammers.%20Browning%20has%20more%20than%204.3%20million%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Media%20O2%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Daisy%20%26quot%3Bcombines%20various%20AI%20models%20which%20work%20together%20to%20listen%20and%20respond%20to%20fraudulent%20calls%20instantaneously%20and%20is%20so%20lifelike%20it%20has%20successfully%20kept%20numerous%20fraudsters%20on%20calls%20for%2040%20minutes%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDaisy%20is%20turning%20the%20tables%20on%20scammers%20%E2%80%94%20outsmarting%20and%20outmaneuvering%20them%20at%20their%20own%20cruel%