nk%20he's%20probably%20under%20pressure%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20and%20if%20he%20has%20a%20couple%20of%20low%20scores%20to%20start%20with%2C%20he%20could%20really%20feel%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20quite%20an%20emotional%20player.%20When%20he's%20up%2C%20he's%20up%2C%20and%20when%20he's%20down%2C%20he%20sort%20of%20struggles%20a%20little%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeam%20India%20is%20undoubtedly%20under%20pressure%20after%20the%200-3%20hammering%20received%20in%20the%20home%20Test%20assignment%20against%20New%20Zealand.%20McGrath%20expects%20Australia%20to%20put%20India%20under%20pressure%20right%20from%20the%20first%20ball%20and%20test%20their%20nerves%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20rut%20they%20are%20presently%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20doubt%2C%20especially%20after%20coming%20off%20a%203-0%20loss%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20you've%20got%20plenty%20of%20ammunition%20to%20back%20yourself%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20McGrath%20asserted%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20put%20the%20pressure%20on%20them%20and%20see%20if%20they're%20up%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20India's%20practice%20sessions%20haven't%20gone%20as%20planned%20in%20Australia%2C%20with%20top%20batters%20like%20Kohli%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc%20struggling%20to%20put%20runs%20on%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731862260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F5mj172