ich%20you%20can%20get%20at%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Bhavan%20along%20with%20your%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20delivering%20her%20keynote%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20congratulate%20Ushaji%2C%20my%20sambandhi%20and%20a%20good%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20who%20gave%20her%20son%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%2C%20a%20great%20route%20to%20identify%20with%20the%20culture%2C%20making%20him%20a%20proud%20British%20citizen%20as%20well%20as%20%5Bhaving%5D%20good%20Indian%20cultural%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20philanthropist%20went%20on%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20British%20Indian%20community%20to%20enable%20the%20work%20of%20Bhavan%20UK's%20cultural%20activities%2C%20%26quot%3Bmentally%2C%20physically%20and%20financially%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20send%20your%20children%20here%20to%20understand%20Indian%20culture%20because%20when%20you%20grow%20old%20you%20go%20towards%20your%20roots...%20that%20gap%20is%20addressed%20by%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Bhavan%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20help%20them%20in%20every%20way%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20staunch%20supporter%20of%20the%20cultural%20centre%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20Vikram%20Doraiswami%2C%20reflected%20upon%20Murty's%20writings%20which%20inspire%20readers%20to%20be%20true%20to%20themselves%20because%20our%20%26quot%3Borigin%20story%20matters%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20trace%20the%20pan-Indian%20message%20of%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Krishna%20story%20is%20relevant%20to%20Diwali%20in%20the%20south%2C%20just%20as%20the%20'Ramayana'%20story%20and%20the%20return%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20Lanka%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20Diwali%20story%20of%20the%20north%20and%20the%20story%20of%20Kali%20Puja%20is%20connected%20with%20the%20story%20of%20Diwali%20in%20the%20east%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%