ia%2C%20with%20fans%20gushing%20over%20the%20adorable%20duo.%20The%20family%20outing%20over%20the%20weekend%20further%20highlighted%20their%20close%20bond.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthis-unseen-photo-of-raha-in-a-pink-swimsuit-posing-with-daddy-ranbir-kapoor-is-the-cutest-thing-you-will-see-on-the-internet-today%2Farticleshow%2F115390444.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Doctor%20Injects%20Partner%20With%20Anaesthesia%20To%20Treat%20Insomnia%2C%20She%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20incident%20in%20southwestern%20China's%20Sichuan%20province%2C%20an%20anesthesiologist%2C%20identified%20by%20his%20surname%20Qu%2C%20has%20been%20implicated%20in%20a%20tragic%20case%20involving%20his%20partner%2C%20Chen%2C%20a%20pharmaceutical%20sales%20representative.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3286714%2Fchina-doctor-kills-insomniac-girlfriend-injecting-anaesthetics-20-times-6-hours%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20caused%20his%20girlfriend's%20death%20by%20attempting%20to%20treat%20her%20insomnia%20with%20repeated%20anaesthetic%20injections.%20He%20administered%20the%20anaesthesia%20more%20than%2020%20times%C2%A0in%20six%20hours%2C%C2%A0leading%20to%20her%20death.%20This%20incident%20has%20sparked%20significant%20online%20outrage%20in%20China%2C%20with%20many%20slamming%20the%20doctor's%20actions%20despite%20his%20claims%20of%20trying%20to%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20two%20met%20through%20an%20online%20dating%20platform%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022.%20Qu%2C%20who%20works%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Jinjiang%20County%2C%20Leshan%2C%20allegedly%20administered%20propofol%2C%20a%20powerful%20anaesthesia%2C%20to%20Chen%20in%20hotel%20rooms%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20between%20September%202023%20and%20March%202024.%20Chen%20had%20requested%20the%20medication%20to%20alleviate%20her%20insomnia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20Qu%20administered%20approximately%201%2C300%20mg%20of%20propofol%20to%20Chen%2C%20through%20her%20ankle%20over%20six%20hours%2C%20from%2011%20pm%20to%205%20am.%20He%20provided%2020%2B%20doses%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20additional%20100%20mg%20for%20her%20to%20use%20later.%20Upon%20returning%20to%20the%20hotel%2C%20Qu%20discovered%20Chen%20had%20died.%C2%A0A%20medical%20examination%20confirmed%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20was%20acute%20propofol%20intoxication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQu%20promptly%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20authorities%2C%20confessed%20to%20his%20actions%2C%20and%20later%20provided%20financial%20compensation%20of%20400%2C000%20yuan%20(US%2455%2C000)%20to%20Chen's%20relatives%2C%20who%20forgave%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Shanghai-based%20representative%20from%20a%20leading%20propofol%20manufacturer%20told%20The%20Post%20that%20propofol%20is%20not%20intended%20for%20treating%20insomnia%20and%20that%20the%20dosages%20used%20in%20this%20case%20drastically%20exceeded%20safe%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPropofol%20is%20a%20short-acting%20general%20anaesthetic%20used%20primarily%20for%20inducing%20and%20maintaining%20general%20anaesthesia%20and%20sedation.%20Typically%2C%20clinical%20doses%20for%20anaesthesia%20induction%20are%201.5-2.5%20mg%20per%20kilogram%20of%20body%20weight.%20For%20maintenance%20of%20anaesthesia%2C%20the%20doses%20usually%20range%20from%204-12%20mg%20per%20kilogram%2C%20while%20sedation%20doses%20vary%20from%201.5-4.5%20mg%20per%20kilogram%2C%20adjusted%20according%20to%20the%20procedure%20and%20patient's%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20injection%20dose%20of%201%2C300%20mg%20is%20significantly%20higher%20than%20standard%20treatment%20protocols.%20Fatalities%20from%20excessive%20use%20of%20anaesthetics%20like%20this%20are%20not%20uncommon.%20Besides%2C%20drug%20abuse%2C%20apart%20from%20safety%20issues%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20addiction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EOn%20November%201%2C%20the%20People's%20Court%20of%20Renshou%20County%20in%20Sichuan%20Province%20delivered%20a%20verdict%2C%20sentencing%20anesthesiologist%20Qu%20to%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20negligent%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20took%20into%20account%20mitigating%20factors%2C%20including%2C%20Qu's%20voluntary%20surrender%20to%20authorities%2C%20his%20full%20confession%2C%20financial%20compensation%20to%20the%20victim's%20family%20and%20the%20family's%20forgiveness.%C2%A0These%20factors%20contributed%20to%20a%20relatively%20lenient%20sentence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731860940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F7gd9kmo8_china-doctor_625x300_17_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-doctor-injects-girlfriend-with-anaesthesia-20-times-in-6-hours-to-treat-insomnia-she-dies-7041910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20caused%20his%20girlfriend's%20death%20by%20attempting%20to%20treat%20her%20insomnia%20with%20repeated%20anaesthetic%20injections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-doctor-injects-girlfriend-with-anaesthesia-20-times-in-6-hours-to-treat-insomnia-she-dies-7041910%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exploring%20favourite%20movies%20of%20'Pushpa'%20star%20Allu%20Arjun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731859937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.