li%3EIt%20is%20being%20used%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20journalism%20or%20artistic%20expression.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20being%20used%20for%20personal%20or%20family%20purposes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBasic%20principles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20data%20collection%20happens%20in%20almost%20every%20online%20activity%20one%20is%20involved%20in.%20Starting%20from%20one%E2%80%99s%20online%20search%2C%20social%20media%20feed%2C%20shopping%20cart%20details%2C%20advertisement%20suggestions%2C%20to%20your%20credit%20card%20details%20and%20UPI%20transactions%2C%20personal%20data%20is%20very%20valuable.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20certain%20systems%20like%20the%20DPDPA%20put%20forth%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20look%20at%20data%20privacy%20basics%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsent%20is%20king%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Ever%20downloaded%20a%20fitness%20app%3F%20Before%20you%20could%20start%20tracking%20your%20steps%2C%20you%20probably%20had%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20long%20list%20of%20terms%20and%20conditions.%20That%E2%80%99s%20consent%20in%20action.%20Under%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20companies%20can%20only%20collect%20your%20personal%20data%20if%20you%E2%80%99ve%20given%20them%20a%20clear%20%E2%80%9Cyes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%20limitation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%E2%80%99s%20say%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20newsletter.%20The%20company%20can%20only%20use%20your%20email%20address%20to%20send%20you%20updates%2C%20not%20to%20target%20you%20with%20ads%20or%20share%20with%20other%20businesses.%20Your%20data%20should%20always%20be%20used%20for%20a%20specific%20purpose.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELess%20is%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20When%20you%20fill%20out%20a%20form%2C%20have%20you%20noticed%20that%20some%20fields%20are%20marked%20as%20optional%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20data%20minimisation%20in%20action.%20Companies%20should%20only%20collect%20the%20data%20they%20absolutely%20need.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20fitness%20app%20might%20need%20your%20height%20and%20weight%20to%20calculate%20your%20BMI%2C%20but%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20your%20Aadhaar%20card%20details.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20time-limit%20on%20data%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Like%20old%20photos%20in%20a%20box%2C%20digital%20data%20can%20also%20become%20outdated.%20The%20DPDPA%20says%20that%20companies%20can%E2%80%99t%20hoard%20your%20data%20forever.%20They%20must%20have%20a%20system%20to%20delete%20it%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20needed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EYour%20data%2C%20your%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20Access%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know%20what%20data%20an%20organisation%20is%20storing%20about%20you.%20You%20can%20contact%20the%20organisation%20or%20website%20at%20any%20time%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20information%20they%20hold.%20Check%20their%20privacy%20policy%20for%20details%20on%20how%20they%20collect%2C%20use%2C%20and%20protect%20your%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20Correction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20incorrect%20data%20about%20you%2C%20you%20can%20request%20corrections.%20A%20consumer-compliant%20redressal%20forum%20under%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20will%20help%20you%20correct%20your%20data%20from%20a%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERight%20to%20Erasure%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20can%20ask%20organisations%20to%20delete%20your%20data%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20needed.%20As%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Officer%20(DPO)%20directly%20for%20data%20protection%20