-proof%20skills%20for%20free.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20content%20that%20was%20easy%20to%20understand%2C%20practical%2C%20and%20specifically%20designed%20to%20address%20the%20unique%20challenges%20we%20face%20when%20building%20something%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20This%20realisation%20became%20the%20catalyst%20for%20LaunchPad%2C%20a%20platform%20created%20to%20fill%20that%20gap%20%E2%80%94%20empowering%20young%20people%20to%20navigate%20the%20complexities%20of%20ideation%2C%20development%2C%20and%20execution%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%2015-year-old%20Aryan%20took%20the%20leap%20and%20started%20LaunchPad%20as%20a%20club%20at%20his%20school.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20small%20group%20of%20students%20learning%20how%20to%20build%20real-world%20projects%20soon%20expanded%20into%20a%20global%20initiative.%20Now%2C%20less%20than%20two%20years%20later%2C%20LaunchPad%20has%20scaled%20beyond%20a%20school%20club%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20serves%20students%20across%2015%20schools%20in%20five%20countries.%20Today%2C%20the%20team%20has%20expanded%20to%20a%20dynamic%20group%20of%2015%20to%2020%20young%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunchPad%E2%80%99s%20mission%20is%20simple%3A%20to%20help%20students%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2017%20learn%20essential%20skills%20and%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20project%20development.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20learning%20how%20to%20code%20or%20design.%20LaunchPad%20focuses%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20future-proof%20skills%20that%20are%20vital%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20fast-changing%20world.%20These%20include%20design%20thinking%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20foundations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20business%20fundamentals%2C%20storytelling%20and%20communication%2C%20and%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20skills%20that%20will%20be%20relevant%20no%20matter%20what%20career%20path%20students%20choose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aryan%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20the%20building%20blocks%20for%20anything%20they%20want%20to%20create%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20interactive%20modules%2C%20videos%2C%20expert%20interviews%2C%20presentations%2C%20and%20quizzes%2C%20LaunchPad%20helps%20students%20learn%20these%20skills%20in%20a%20fun%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20effective%20way.%20Each%20module%20includes%20a%20guided%20assignment%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20students%20build%20their%20first%20project%20step-by-step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20design%20thinking%20module%2C%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%20their%20passions%20through%20exercises%20like%20the%20Ikigai%20exercise%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20find%20the%20overlap%20between%20what%20they%20love%2C%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%20and%20what%20problems%20they%20can%20solve%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasises%20that%20LaunchPad%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20accessible%20and%20engaging.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20content%20is%20designed%20for%20teenagers%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20too%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20too%20basic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20students%20to%20feel%20like%20they%E2%80%99re%20learning%20real%2C%20practical%20skills%20that%20they%20can%20apply%20at%20their%20workplace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20early%20challenges%3A%20Launching%20the%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20platform%20like%20LaunchPad%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20hurdles%20Aryan%20faced%20was%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20get%20approval%20for%20the%20idea%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20to%20spark%20interest%20among%20students%20about%20the%20website.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20pitched%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20went%20from%20class%20to%20class%2C%20speaking%20with%20students%20and%20noting%20down%20their%20names%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20many%20of%20the%20same%20obstacles%20that%20any%20young%20entrepreneur%20faces%20when%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20community.%20He%20realised%20that%20in%20order%20to%20grow%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20increase%20the%20click-through%20rate%20on%20the%20website%20and%20boost%20user%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20by%20experimenting%20with%20our%20marketing.%20I%20created%20Instagram%20reels%20and%20made%20posts%20for%20our%20LinkedIn%20page.%20That%20really%20helped%20us%20get%20the%20word%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202900px)%20100vw%2C%202900px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20snapshot%20of%20Launchpad's%20website%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024.jpg%202900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-300x170.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-500x283.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-768x435.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-1536x871.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-2048x1161.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-1200x680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FStill-of-LaunchPad-Website-1_11zon-1-1731419024-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-379457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20hurdles%20Aryan%20faced%20was%20sparking%20interest%20among%20students%20about%20the%20website.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20was%20the%20development%20of%20the%20platform%20itself.%20Aryan%20had%20limited%20experience%20with%20coding%20but%20made%20use%20of%20no-code%20platforms%20that%20allowed%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20front-end%20design%20while%20his%20friends%20helped%20with%20the%20back-end%20coding.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20a%20lot%20along%20the%20way.%20But%20my%20friends%20really%20helped%20me%20fine-tune%20the%20website%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20perfectionist%20tendencies%2C%20Aryan%20knew%20the%20importance%20of%20launching%20before%20everything%20was%20perfect.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20delayed%20the%20launch%20by%20a%20month%20because%20I%20wanted%20everything%20to%20look%20just%20right.%20But%20eventually%2C%20we%20had%20to%20launch%20and%20ju