0questions%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Revise%20frequently%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20chapter%20must%20be%20revised%20at%20least%20five%20to%20six%20times%20before%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalpit.%20He%20believes%20that%20regular%20revision%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20habits%20for%20any%20top%20scorer.%20Revisiting%20each%20chapter%20several%20times%20throughout%20the%20year%20helps%20reinforce%20your%20memory%20and%20solidify%20understanding.%20Kalpit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20revised%20chapters%20multiple%20times%20to%20ensure%20nothing%20was%20left%20to%20chance%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20students%20should%20also%20do%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Develop%20and%20practise%20a%20clear%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20suggests%20that%20students%20should%20develop%20their%20exam%20strategy%20well%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20big%20day.%20%E2%80%9CSolve%20plenty%20of%20test%20papers%20at%20home%2C%20at%20your%20own%20pace%2C%20and%20identify%20which%20subjects%20come%20more%20naturally%20to%20you.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20decide%20which%20ones%20to%20tackle%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20know%20how%20much%20time%20to%20allocate%20to%20each%20section%2C%20when%20to%20skip%20difficult%20questions%2C%20and%20how%20to%20adapt%20your%20approach%20based%20on%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-07-at-15.13.20-1-1731054457-500x495-1-1731055728.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%